    Interface Description
    Listable<K>

    This class produces an unmodifiable map of the elements inside the object, in a key, value fashion
  • Class Summary

    JedisPoolAdapter
    This class creates a new 'pool' of redis connections from only one existing connection.
    JedisSentinelPoolAdapter
    This class creates a new 'pool' of redis connections from a sentinel pool This is an adapter for This class is not, in any way, thread safe.

    A map.entry implementation Immutable, as setValue is not implemented
    SimplePubSub
